files.description: 10-page PDF: Export Format Documentation. Describes C-CDA XML export (16 sections covering standard clinical data) plus a proprietary CSV format for advanced demographics and remaining EHI. No data dictionary, no field definitions, no sample files. Generic C-CDA explanations paraphrased from HL7. Copyright 2023, created in Google Docs.
